headline: Harbor Long-Short Equity ETF Q1 2025 Commentary
summary: During Q1 2025, the Harbor Long-Short Equity ETF returned 5.23% (NAV), outperforming its benchmark, the HRFX Equity Hedge Index, which returned 0.22%.
